//================
//Approximate performance hit
//Free: 
//Light: VIGNETTE, BLOOM(<= 2 samples)
//Medium: ACARTOON, BLOOM(== 3 samples)
//Heavy: BLOOM(>= 4 samples)
//Extremely Heavy: BLOOM(>= 8 samples)
